NK005(ca)004:0: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)004:1: gyi cho ga kun tu bzang po'i zhal lung zhes
NK005(ca)004:4: dpal sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba rigs
NK005(ca)004:5: bsdus pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga kun tu bzang
NK005(ca)004:6: po'i zhal lung zhes bya ba /
NK005(ca)004:7: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK005(ca)004:8: dpal mchog dang po'i mgon po kun tu bzang //
NK005(ca)004:9: sku dang gsung thugs bkod pa mi zad sprin //
NK005(ca)004:10: sangs rgyas kun dang mnyam sbyor rigs drug gi //
NK005(ca)004:11: 'khor lor snang mdzad bla mar phyag bagyi'o //
NK005(ca)004:12: gang gi snying po'i dkyil 'khor rab yangs par //
NK005(ca)004:13: skal bzang myur bder 'jug pa thabs kyi sgo //
NK005(ca)004:14: rnam dag gzhung don bla ma'i man ngag bzhin //
NK005(ca)004:15: kun tu bzang po'i zhal lung 'dir gsal bya //
NK005(ca)004:22: bde chen sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos //
NK005(ca)004:23: rdo rje sems dpa' dpal gyi lha //
NK005(ca)004:24: rnam pa sna tshogs kun gyi mchog /
NK005(ca)004:26: gsang ba mchog gi dgyes par ni //
NK005(ca)004:27: thams cad bdag nyid rjes su bsgrub //
NK005(ca)004:28: zhes gsungs pas gzhi'i rgyud ces bya ba gdul bya'i
NK005(ca)004:29: rgyud kyis bsdus pa gzhi 'bras gnyis su med pa'i
NK005(ca)004:30: de kho na nyid mngon du byed pa nas thun
NK005(ca)004:31: mong gi dngos grub gang la dmigs pa de'i bar
NK005(ca)004:33: rten gnas phun sum tshogs ldan pas //
NK005(ca)004:34: sngon 'gro'i bsnyen pa rdzogs byas te //
NK005(ca)004:35: sa gzhi sta gon gnas pa dang //
NK005(ca)004:36: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor rtsom sgrub cing //
NK005(ca)004:37: 'jug pa'i sbyin sreg gtor ma'i las //
NK005(ca)004:38: rab gnas dbang bskur la sogs rnams //
NK005(ca)004:39: bdag gzhan smin cing grol ba'i phyir //
NK005(ca)004:40: dam pa'i lung bzhin bsgrub par bya //
NK005(ca)004:41: zhes pas gzhi'i rgyud de glo bur gyi dri ma'i
NK005(ca)004:42: sbugs las grol bar byed pa thabs kyi rgyud ces
NK005(ca)004:43: bya ba lam gyi dngos po yan lag dang bcas
NK005(ca)004:44: pas bsdus pa las 'dir dkyil 'khor gyi bya ba
NK005(ca)004:45: sngon du 'gro bas de nyid sgrub cing mchod pa'i
NK005(ca)004:47: de la yang sbyor ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:49: mjug gi bya ba dang gsum du gnas pa las /
NK005(ca)004:50: dang po la yang las kyi gzhi bzung ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:51: las kyi rim pa dngos la 'jug pa'o //
NK005(ca)004:53: rten gyi gang zag zhi zhing des pa sogs rgyud dag cing byang chub du sems bskyed pa /
NK005(ca)004:54: shes rab gsum gyis drang nges kyi don khong du chud pa /
NK005(ca)004:55: dkyil 'khor 'dir dbang gis smin cing dam tshig la
NK005(ca)004:56: gnas pa 'gro ba sgrol ba'i snying stobs dang ldan
NK005(ca)004:57: pas sgrub thabs bzhin gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK005(ca)004:59: dkyil 'khor gzhan lnga'i gtso bo la khri dang /
NK005(ca)004:60: 'khor gyi lha mo rnams la stong lta bu'i grangs kyi bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:61: dus dang mtshan ma dang gnang ba thob pa dang
NK005(ca)004:62: 'gog pa med pas kyang rung ste sngon du goms
NK005(ca)004:63: par byas nas / rgyal thebs sogs sgrub pa'i grogs
NK005(ca)004:64: dang bcas te gnas dus yo byad sogs phun sum
NK005(ca)004:65: tshogs pa'i cha rkyen thams cad bzang zhing tshogs par
NK005(ca)004:66: par byas nas / bya ba'o // gnyis pa la sa'i cho ga dang /
NK005(ca)004:67: sta gon gyi cho ga gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)004:68: dang po'i sa'i cho ga la lnga las /
NK005(ca)004:69: dang po la spyir brtag pa dang bye brag tu brtag pa gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)004:71: yid dang mthun pa'i gnas kyi gzhi pad+ma 'dra ba
NK005(ca)004:72: las dbus mtho zhing shar dang byang du gzhol ba
NK005(ca)004:73: nam mkha'i 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad pa ltar mngon pa
NK005(ca)004:74: nags tshal bzang po me tog dang 'bras bus brgyan
NK005(ca)004:75: pa sogs sgrub pa'i gnas su gsung pa bzhin /
NK005(ca)004:77: gzhi der pus nub tsam du bskos nas slar sa des gang ba'am /
NK005(ca)004:78: dri bzang po dang sbyar ba'i chus bkang ste /
NK005(ca)004:79: mnyam par bzhag pas rdor dril bzung nas rang sngags
NK005(ca)004:80: brjod bzhin du mi drag par gom pa brgya'i gnas
NK005(ca)004:81: nas log ste bltas pas ngan pa'i mtshan ma mthong
NK005(ca)004:82: na gzhan du spo ba'am sbyin sreg gis sbyang bar
NK005(ca)004:83: bya zhing / rnam shes dang ye shes kyi phyag rgyas kyang brtag par bshad do //
NK005(ca)004:84: gnyis pa la snang ba dang mi snang ba la bslang ba gnyis las /
NK005(ca)004:86: brtags pas rung ba'i sa de rgyal po sogs la
NK005(ca)004:87: bslang ba'am rim gyis nyos nas rang dbang du byas
NK005(ca)004:89: gzhi de rang byung dang dri bzang bdud rtsi lnga la sogs pa'i man+dala byas la /
NK005(ca)004:90: me tog gi tshom bu dgod /
NK005(ca)004:91: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang gtor ma cha gnyis bshams la /
NK005(ca)004:92: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi bdag po'i rnal 'byor bsgom
NK005(ca)004:93: pa sngon du 'gro bas mchod gtor rnams byin gyis
NK005(ca)004:94: brlab nas sa bdag rnams tshim par byas te /
NK005(ca)004:95: sa bdag lha klu 'khor bcas rnams //
NK005(ca)004:96: bdag gi bsnyen sgrub ma thon par //
NK005(ca)004:97: khyed la gnas 'di bdag g.yar gyis //
NK005(ca)004:98: ci bde bar ni gnang du gsol //
NK005(ca)004:99: zhes bslang zhing bsod nams kyi dpung bskyed pa'i phyir rten dgram /
NK005(ca)004:101: mchod sbyin sogs kyang ci 'grub bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:102: gsum pa sa sbyang zhing rlob pa ni /
NK005(ca)004:103: sa der byin gyis brlabs pa'i dri chab sngags kyis gtor zhing /
NK005(ca)004:104: ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i 'phro 'dus bdud rtsi'i rdzas dang yi ge gsum gyis sbyangs nas /
NK005(ca)004:105: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi gsar du sgrub na /
NK005(ca)004:107: de'i lto ba las cung zad mdun gyi cha nas dang por brko zhing /
NK005(ca)004:108: de nas dkyil 'khor ji tsam 'dod pa'i rgyar dngos
NK005(ca)004:109: grub rab 'bring gi don du khru do dang khru
NK005(ca)004:110: gang dang sor bzhi'i tshad du brko zhing rus pa
NK005(ca)004:111: dang gseg ma dang gyo mo dang sol ba sogs
NK005(ca)004:113: dri zhim po'i chu dang sa mnyen 'jam zhing spyin
NK005(ca)004:114: pa dag bsres nas lnga tshan lnga'i rdzas rnams snying
NK005(ca)004:115: por bcug la dkyil 'khor gyi rgya las nyis 'gyur
NK005(ca)004:117: sngon nas dul ba'i sa yin na brko ba sogs mi dgos /
NK005(ca)004:118: gang gi tshe yang chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i don bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)004:119: swa b+h+aa wa'i sngags brjod de dri'i chus byug go //
NK005(ca)004:121: rigs kyi rgyan dang ldan pas /
NK005(ca)004:123: zhes sa gzhi nam mkha'i rang bzhin du gyur /
NK005(ca)004:124: der 'byung bzhi'i dkyil 'khor ri rab dang bcas shing
NK005(ca)004:125: rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa gur me 'od dang bcas
NK005(ca)004:126: par bsam nas sna tshogs rdo rje'i phyag rgya bcings
NK005(ca)004:128: me 'di ni badz+ri b+ha wa badz+ra ban+d+ha h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:130: bzhi pa dpang po gsol ba ni /
NK005(ca)004:131: thal mo lan gsum sa la brdabs pas rang gi
NK005(ca)004:132: mdun du sa'i lha mo sku mdog ser mo bum
NK005(ca)004:133: pa 'dzin pa bka' nyan pa'i tshul du gnas pa
NK005(ca)004:134: la / zhabs bsil dang nyer spyod rol mo gtor ma rnams phul nas /
NK005(ca)004:135: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK005(ca)004:136: spyod pa'i tshul dang khyad par gyi //
NK005(ca)004:137: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK005(ca)004:138: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK005(ca)004:139: skyob pa sh+aakya seng ge yis //
NK005(ca)004:140: ji ltar bdud kyi sde bcom pa //
NK005(ca)004:141: de bzhin bdag gis bdud las ni //
NK005(ca)004:142: rgyal bar bya phyir dkyil 'khor bri //
NK005(ca)004:143: zhes lan gsum gyis ji srid las ma grub kyi bar du bzhugs par gsol bas /
NK005(ca)004:144: lha mo dgyes pa'i mdangs phyung ste /
NK005(ca)004:145: slob dpon chen po dkyil 'khor mdzod //
NK005(ca)004:146: dga' ba chen pos las sgrubs shig /
NK005(ca)004:148: slar yang de nyid du thim par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)004:149: lnga pa la bsrung bar gsol ba gdab pa dang bsrung ba dngos las /
NK005(ca)004:151: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi'i dbus su slob dpon rgyan bcu
NK005(ca)004:152: gnyis kyis brgyan cing rdor dril bzung ste gtso bo'i
NK005(ca)004:153: nga rgyal gyis gnas pa la /
NK005(ca)004:154: phyogs bzhi'i slob ma lha mo bzhi'i nga rgyal 'dzin pas rim bzhin //
NK005(ca)004:155: byams chen nam mkha'i rigs sbyor ba //
NK005(ca)004:157: rnam 'byed gsal ba'i chos mchog can //
NK005(ca)004:158: yang dag ye shes spyod pas grol //
NK005(ca)004:160: thugs rje'i gnas mchog dag pa'i dngos //
NK005(ca)004:161: mnyam nyid chos kun 'byung ba'i gzhi //
NK005(ca)004:162: yon tan rin chen mchog ston pa'i //
NK005(ca)004:163: rnam 'phrul chos las rab tu grol //
NK005(ca)004:165: dga' ba'i pad+mo mtshan ldan pa //
NK005(ca)004:166: kun rtog dngos gsal chad pa med //
NK005(ca)004:167: rdo rje gsang gsum sngags don pa'i //
NK005(ca)004:170: btang snyoms gnas ngan d+r+wa ba sel //
NK005(ca)004:171: phrin las bzhi po stobs dang ldan //
NK005(ca)004:172: bya ba'i ye shes mthar mdzad cing //
NK005(ca)004:173: sprul pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan du gsol //
NK005(ca)004:174: a la la hoh zhes so so dang thun mong du //
NK005(ca)004:175: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)004:177: sdig pa thams cad las grol zhing //
NK005(ca)004:178: bsod nams dngos grub kun 'byung ba'i //
NK005(ca)004:179: rgyal ba kun gyi 'byung gnas mchog /
NK005(ca)004:180: mthong dga' thos pas grol byed pa //
NK005(ca)004:181: lam mchog gsang ba chen po'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)004:182: bdag nyid chen pos bstan du gsol //
NK005(ca)004:183: a la la hoh zhes gsol ba gdab cing /
NK005(ca)004:184: bzhi med na gcig gis kyang phyogs de dag tu song nas bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:185: gnyis pa srung ba dang mtshams bcad pa gnyis kyi dang po ni /
NK005(ca)004:186: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa'i ting nge 'dzin las
NK005(ca)004:187: skad cig gis rta mchog rol pa'i khro bo 'jigs
NK005(ca)004:188: shing rngams pa mi bzad pa'i khro bo'i sprin spro
NK005(ca)004:189: ba'i mig g.yas su ma las nyi ma dang /
NK005(ca)004:190: g.yon du a las zla ba /
NK005(ca)004:191: sna rtser yam las byung ba'i rlung gis mtshan par gyur /
NK005(ca)004:192: bgegs rnams nyi ma las byung ba'i mes bsreg zla
NK005(ca)004:193: ba las byung ba'i chus bkrus sna rtse'i rlung gis
NK005(ca)004:195: mig gi rdzi ma 'dren pa 'bar ba'i lta stangs
NK005(ca)004:196: kyis blta zhing rdo rje gsor ba dang dril bu
NK005(ca)004:198: zhes brjod pas khro bo dang mtshon cha'i sprin spro bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)004:200: lha klu gnod sbyin 'byung po dang //
NK005(ca)004:201: dri za srin po sha za'i tshogs //
NK005(ca)004:202: gshin rje ma mo mkha' 'gro gdug /
NK005(ca)004:203: gnod byed drag po ma lus rnams //
NK005(ca)004:204: gang dag sa gzhi 'dir gnas pa //
NK005(ca)004:205: srung byed sa yi bdag po'i bka' //
NK005(ca)004:206: thos pa tsam gyis myur du dengs //
NK005(ca)004:207: nga yi bka' las 'da' ma byed //
NK005(ca)004:208: gang zhig gnas pa'i mthu bo che //
NK005(ca)004:209: rdo rje tho ba kha t+w+aam kas //
NK005(ca)004:210: thal ba'i tshogs bzhin bshig par byed //
NK005(ca)004:213: gal te gang gi dam tshig bcag /
NK005(ca)004:216: zhes lan gsum brjod cing sa gzhi bskor //
NK005(ca)004:217: rol mo'i sgra dang yungs thun gyis brab pa sogs drag po'i tsham rngams kyang bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:218: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su 'dug ste phur
NK005(ca)004:219: bu dar gyi cod pan can bcu mdun du bkod
NK005(ca)004:220: / rang gi thugs ka nas khro bo 'dod pa'i
NK005(ca)004:221: rgyal po spros phyogs bcu'i bgegs rnams sum+b+ha dang rang
NK005(ca)004:222: sngags kyis bkug pa'i gzugs la gzhugs pa'i sems phab
NK005(ca)004:223: / ste / slar yang rang gi snying ga nas khro bo bcu spros phur bu rnams la bstim /
NK005(ca)004:224: khro bo so so'i sngags dang /
NK005(ca)004:225: g+ha g+ha ta ya sogs kyis phyogs bcu'i bgegs la
NK005(ca)004:226: phur bu'i tshul du btab pas de rnams kyi lus
NK005(ca)004:227: phug ste g.yo 'gul med cing 'od gsal bar bsam
NK005(ca)004:228: pa sogs sgrub thabs bzhin dbang ldan nas brtsams te
NK005(ca)004:229: gdab par bya'o // bsdu na phyogs skyong bcu gnas lngar bsdus te /
NK005(ca)004:230: khro bo chen po stobs chen dang sprin sgra la
NK005(ca)004:231: sogs pa'i phur bu g+ha ta'i sngags kyis btab pas
NK005(ca)004:233: gang gi tshe yang phur bus btab pa'i rjes de
NK005(ca)004:234: nyid du he ru ka lha mo'i 'khor dang bcas
NK005(ca)004:236: rkang pa bskyod nas lag pa bskyod //
NK005(ca)004:237: cung zad ngo mtshar zur mig tshul //
NK005(ca)004:238: zhes sogs gsungs pa bzhin rdo rje'i gar dang stangs
NK005(ca)004:239: stabs kyi rol pa ci rigs pas bcag cing bsrung
NK005(ca)004:241: las kyi rdo rjes phyi rol gyi stegs bur mchod
NK005(ca)004:242: gtor bshams nas phyogs skyong dang sde brgyad lan chags
NK005(ca)004:243: la gtor ma bsngo bar gsungs pa ni cha gsum
NK005(ca)004:244: gyi cho ga bzhin du byas pas 'grub bo //
NK005(ca)004:245: khyad par rgyal po chen po sde bzhi la gtor
NK005(ca)004:246: ma phul zhing rten la bzhag nas mnga' gsol bar
NK005(ca)004:247: gsungs pa ni rigs mthun gyi cho ga gang bde
NK005(ca)004:249: sngar bshad pa'i sa'i cho ga phal cher dkyil 'khor khang pa logs su byed pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:250: rkos nas stegs bu bya dgos pa'i sar yin la /
NK005(ca)004:251: gzhan du mi snang ba las bslang ba tsam sngon du 'gro bas /
NK005(ca)004:252: rdzas sngags ting nge 'dzin gyis sbyong zhing dpang po
NK005(ca)004:253: gsol nas bsrung ba'i las la 'jug pa yin no
NK005(ca)004:254: // de dag ni nub dang po'i bya ba'o //
NK005(ca)004:255: gsum pa sta gon la lha slob ma bum pa sta gon dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)004:257: gzhi der rgyar 'dom gang la sogs pa'i stegs bu brtsigs pa'am /
NK005(ca)004:258: de dang mnyam pa'i gzhi la ba byung lnga dang dri bzang bsres pa byug /
NK005(ca)004:259: de'i steng du byin gyis brlabs pa'i bdud rtsis byugs
NK005(ca)004:260: la lha gnas mi 'chol ba'i skya thig tsam btab
NK005(ca)004:261: nas / bdud rtsi lngas gtso gnas su gru bzhi
NK005(ca)004:262: dang 'khor gnas su thig le zlum por byas la
NK005(ca)004:263: so so'i sngags kyis me tog dgram /
NK005(ca)004:264: de'i mtha' mchod pa'i tshogs kyis bskor /
NK005(ca)004:265: skabs don dang 'brel na rtsa dkyil gyi phyogs bzhir sbyin sreg gi thab khung bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:266: mtshams su rta mchog lhag ma'i dkyil 'khor yang bsham mo //
NK005(ca)004:267: de nas mchod pa byin gyis brlabs de bsrung 'khor nas gzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:268: rten dang brten pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor gsal btab /
NK005(ca)004:270: mdun gyi dkyil 'khor mnyes par byas nas bstod pa
NK005(ca)004:271: bya bar gsungs pa ni sgrub thabs las shes par
NK005(ca)004:272: 'gyur zhing / skabs don 'jug pa bde ba'i dbang du ni /
NK005(ca)004:273: dkyil 'khor gyi gzhi dngas shing thogs pa med pa la /
NK005(ca)004:274: tshom bu rnams lha so so'i gdan ji lta ba bzhin 'grub par gyur /
NK005(ca)004:275: dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i lte bar dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen po zhes pa nas /
NK005(ca)004:276: bzang mo dang mnyam par sbyor ba'o'i bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:277: de'i phyogs bzhir bde mchog ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:278: de'i phyi'i shar sogs phyogs bzhir sangs rgyas byang chub ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:279: me sogs mtshams bzhir gling bu ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:280: grwa bzhir me tog ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:281: sgo bzhi'i gnas su rta mgrin 'phang mtho ma sogs bzhi rnams g.yas bskor gyis 'khod /
NK005(ca)004:282: dkyil 'khor shar ma'i dbus su rgyal ba rtag pa rnam par snang mdzad nas /
NK005(ca)004:283: rdo rje skyil mo krung gis bzhugs pa'o'i bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:284: phyogs bzhir sangs rgyas kun brjod ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:285: de'i phyi'i shar sogs phyogs bzhir sangs rgyas kun ldan ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:286: me sogs mtshams bzhir gling bu ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:287: grwa bzhir me tog ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:288: sgo bzhi'i gnas su sgo skyong bzhi rnams g.yas bskor gyis 'khod /
NK005(ca)004:289: dkyil 'khor lho ma'i dbus su dpal chen po he ru ka nas /
NK005(ca)004:290: ba dan rtse gsum pa'i phyag rgya can gyis 'khyud pa'o'i bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:291: de'i phyogs bzhir go r+ai ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:292: mtshams bzhir tsan+da l+ai sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:293: phyi'i me sogs mtshams bzhir mda' 'dzan ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:294: gra bzhir sgo bzhi'i gnas su sgo skyong bzhi rnams g.yas bskor gyis 'khod /
NK005(ca)004:295: dkyil 'khor nub ma'i dbus su pad+ma gar gyi dbang phyug nas /
NK005(ca)004:296: rol pa'i stabs kyis bzhugs pa'o'i bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:297: de'i phyogs bzhir rnam gzigs ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:298: phyi'i shar sogs phyogs bzhir gtum pa'i dbang phyug ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:299: me sogs mtshams bzhir gling bu ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:300: gra bzhir sgo bzhi'i gnas su sgo skyong bzhi rnams g.yas bskor gyis 'khod /
NK005(ca)004:301: dkyil 'khor byang ma'i dbus su rdo rje nyi ma nas /
NK005(ca)004:302: rin po che dang thod pa 'dzin pa dang 'khril pa'o'i bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:303: de'i phyogs bzhir dbang bskur ma sogs bzhi dang /
NK005(ca)004:304: phyi'i shar sogs phyogs bzhir mda' gzhu ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:305: me sogs mtshams bzhir gling bu ma sogs bzhi /
NK005(ca)004:306: gra bzhir sgo bzhi'i gnas su sgo skyong bzhi rnams g.yas bskor gyis 'khod /
NK005(ca)004:307: mtshams bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su rta mchog rol pa'i sangs rgyas nas /
NK005(ca)004:309: de'i g.yas g.yon du sna tshogs pad+mo ma dang sna
NK005(ca)004:310: tshogs rdo rje ma gnyis kyis lhag pa las 'khor
NK005(ca)004:311: gzhan rnams ni phrin las kyi bye brag las phyogs
NK005(ca)004:312: mtshams zung re rigs dang mtshungs par snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)004:313: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi dpral bar /
NK005(ca)004:315: snying ga'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas ye
NK005(ca)004:316: shes kyi 'khor lo badz+ra sa m+aa dzah dzahh+aum bam
NK005(ca)004:317: hoh e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa k+aa
NK005(ca)004:318: ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam
NK005(ca)004:321: dzahh+aum bam hoh k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK005(ca)004:322: zhes dam tshig pa la bstim /
NK005(ca)004:323: +aahh+aum a ti p+au hoh zhes pa nas /
NK005(ca)004:324: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK005(ca)004:325: zhes pa'i bar sgrub thabs kyi dkyus ltar las /
NK005(ca)004:326: ji ltar rigs pas mchod cing bstod nas /
NK005(ca)004:327: spos dang bcas pa'i rdor dril 'dzin bzhin pas /
NK005(ca)004:328: thugs rje chen po bcom ldan 'das //
NK005(ca)004:329: ma lus sems can don mdzad pa'i //
NK005(ca)004:330: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor sras dang bcas //
NK005(ca)004:331: stobs mchog rgyal chen rnams la bstod //
NK005(ca)004:332: sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam sbyor ba'i //
NK005(ca)004:334: mgon gyur las rnams grub pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)004:335: rdo rje gsang ba bdag gis bri //
NK005(ca)004:336: slob ma rnams la brtse phyir dang //
NK005(ca)004:337: bdag nyid che rnams mchod pa'i phyir //
NK005(ca)004:338: bcom ldan khyod la bdag gus te //
NK005(ca)004:339: dgyes mdzad 'os par gyur lags pas //
NK005(ca)004:340: thams cad bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)004:341: bya ba chen po'i 'khor lo'i phyir //
NK005(ca)004:342: byang chub sems dpa' 'bras gnas dang //
NK005(ca)004:343: gang gzhan sngags kyi lha rnams dang //
NK005(ca)004:345: rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi rjes dga' ba //
NK005(ca)004:346: bstan la gnas pa'i 'gro ba dang //
NK005(ca)004:347: gangs su rdo rje'i spyan mnga' ba //
NK005(ca)004:349: don grub gsang ba bdag gis brtsams //
NK005(ca)004:350: rjes su brtse bar nyer dgongs te //
NK005(ca)004:351: gnang bar mdzad pa'i 'os lags so //
NK005(ca)004:352: zhes lan gsum gyis snyan gsan phul nas /
NK005(ca)004:354: shap+da'i bar gyi mchod de brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NK005(ca)004:355: 'grub na skabs 'dir sbyin sreg kyang bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:356: gnyis pa slob ma sta gon ni dbang chog tu shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:357: gsum pa bum pa sta gon ni /
NK005(ca)004:358: rin po che dang las byas pa'i bum pa mtshan nyid dang ldan pa lha grangs dang mnyam pa'am /
NK005(ca)004:359: ma 'byor na 'khor lo drug la re re dang las bum ste bdun /
NK005(ca)004:360: de yang ma 'byor na rnam rgyal dang las bum gnyis su byas la /
NK005(ca)004:361: gu gul gyis bdug cing bgegs bskrad /
NK005(ca)004:362: mgul chings sogs chas su bcug /
NK005(ca)004:363: rdzas nyer lnga dang bcas pa'i dri bzang gi chus bkang ba dkyil 'khor gyi gnas su bzhag /
NK005(ca)004:366: stong pa'i ngang las b+h+r+aum las ye shes rin po
NK005(ca)004:367: che'i rang bzhin can gyi bum pa mtshan nyid thams
NK005(ca)004:368: cad yongs su rdzogs pa'i gzhal yas khang gi rnam
NK005(ca)004:369: rgyal bum pa'i nang du rigs drug gi dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)004:370: so so'i gdan dang bcas par gyur /
NK005(ca)004:371: dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i gnas su dpal rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba chen po zhes pa nas /
NK005(ca)004:372: dkyil 'khor byang ma'i rdo rje nyi ma nas /
NK005(ca)004:373: thod pa 'dzin pa dang 'khril pa'o'i bar sngar ltar dang /
NK005(ca)004:374: mtshams bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi gnas dang las bum gyi nang du rta mchog rol pa'i sangs rgyas nas /
NK005(ca)004:375: nges par 'khyud pa'o zhes pa'i bar gyis gtso bo
NK005(ca)004:376: rnams kyi bskyed tshig brjod pas 'khor zhar bskyed byas
NK005(ca)004:377: pas khyab cing bskyed tshig byed na lha sta gon
NK005(ca)004:378: bzhin dang las bum gyi lha la 'khor mi dgos
NK005(ca)004:380: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi dpral bar sogs nas /
NK005(ca)004:381: a ti pu ho zhes pa'i bar gyis spyan 'dren mchod bstim phyag rnams sta gon gzhin dang /
NK005(ca)004:382: de nas ji ltar rigs pa'i mchod pa dang bstod pa byas nas gzungs thag la 'jus te /
NK005(ca)004:383: bdag gi zhal nas sngags kyi phreng ba gzungs thag la 'khril te song /
NK005(ca)004:384: bum pa'i lha rnams kyi thugs rgyud bskul /
NK005(ca)004:385: snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang sems ye shes kyi bdud rtsir babs pas bum pa gang bar bsam zhing /
NK005(ca)004:386: rnam rgyal du 'khor los bsgyur ba drug gi snying
NK005(ca)004:387: po rnams gtso 'khor gyi 'gros sbyor ba ci nus
NK005(ca)004:388: dang / las bum du rta mchog gi sngags brgya
NK005(ca)004:389: rtsa sogs bzlas nas slar yang mchod de me tog
NK005(ca)004:390: dang bcas pa'i mchod yon phul bas /
NK005(ca)004:391: lha thams cad chags pa chen pos ye shes kyi
NK005(ca)004:392: bdud rtsir zhu ba bum chu dang ro gcig tu
NK005(ca)004:394: spos kyis bdug nas bgegs skrod pa dang mchod cing bsrung bar bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:395: de yang slob ma dang dbang bskur dang rab gnas dang bdag 'jug dkyus ma dang /
NK005(ca)004:396: sgrub pa dngos grub kyi dbang len pa rnams la bum pa nges par dgos la /
NK005(ca)004:397: sgrub mchod tsam pa ni bum pa nges par dgos pa min yang 'grub na ni legs so //
NK005(ca)004:398: de dag ni nub gnyis pa'i bya ba'o //
NK005(ca)004:400: dkyil 'khor mngon par 'du bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:401: der rang gzhan gyi don sgrub pa'o //
NK005(ca)004:402: dang po la thig gdab pa /
NK005(ca)004:404: rgyan dgram pa dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)004:406: nangs par sta gon gyi lha mchod de /
NK005(ca)004:407: be g+aa pra ma yam zhes 'degs pa'i rgyas nam mkhar btegs nas bkod la /
NK005(ca)004:408: tshom bu dang mchod pa rnams gzhan du bsal /
NK005(ca)004:409: thig skud kha dog lnga pa srid du dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)004:410: las nyis 'gyur spoms su sgo'i nyi shu cha yod
NK005(ca)004:411: pa thod pa'am rin po che'i snod du bzhag pa
NK005(ca)004:412: bsang sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las hihh+r+aihtram h+aam lnga
NK005(ca)004:413: las byung ba'i srad bu dkar sngo dmar ser ljang
NK005(ca)004:414: khu rnams de bzhin gshegs pa rigs lnga'i skur gyur
NK005(ca)004:415: bsang sbyangs / / rang gi mig gnyis dzah yig
NK005(ca)004:416: las byung ba'i nyi zla 'bar ba'i lta stangs dang
NK005(ca)004:417: bsang sbyangs / / / d+aip+ta drish+ta ang+ku sha dza dzah zhes pas /
NK005(ca)004:418: nam mkhar bzhugs pa'i de bzhin gshegs pa rnams kyi
NK005(ca)004:419: thugs ka nas ye shes kyi thig 'od zer lnga'i
NK005(ca)004:420: rang bzhin du byung ba dam tshig pa la gnyis
NK005(ca)004:422: pany+tsa ku la sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham nas shap+da'i bar gyis mchod /
NK005(ca)004:423: chos sku nam mkha' mas bstod /
NK005(ca)004:425: badz+ra sa ma ya s+au tra ma ti kra ma h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:426: +aahh+aum gis brtan par byas nas slob dpon shar dang slob ma nub tu gnas pa las /
NK005(ca)004:427: +aahh+aum dzahdzahdzahzhesa thig skud brkyang ba gtad la yab kyi
NK005(ca)004:428: gsang ba nas yum gyi mkhar byang chub sems kyi
NK005(ca)004:430: stobs mchog dpa' bo dgongs su gsol //
NK005(ca)004:431: rdo rje thig gi sgra ldan pas //
NK005(ca)004:432: nam mkha'i dkyil 'khor legs grub cing //
NK005(ca)004:433: 'gro ba'i don la bskul bar mdzad //
NK005(ca)004:434: bo d+hi tsit+ta sarba sat+wa h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:435: zhes brjod cing drangs nas lte ba'i thad kyi bar
NK005(ca)004:436: snang la rdo rje dang bcas pa'i g.yas pa'i mtheb
NK005(ca)004:437: mdzub kyis se gol dang bcas pas /
NK005(ca)004:438: badz+ra sa ma ya s+w+au tra ma tikra ma h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:439: zhes tshangs thig dang po gdab /
NK005(ca)004:440: de bzhin du tshangs thig gnyis pa sogs btab pas
NK005(ca)004:441: nam mkha' la gzhal yas khang lhun gyis grub par
NK005(ca)004:442: bsam zhing / de dang mthun par sa gzhi la yang gdab par bya ste /
NK005(ca)004:443: tshangs pa'i thig gi phyogs bzhi ru //
NK005(ca)004:444: cha chen dgu dgu bco brgyad las //
NK005(ca)004:445: tshangs thig nas bzung dang po dang //
NK005(ca)004:446: bdun pa phyed gdab phyi ma bsil //
NK005(ca)004:447: gnyis pa brgyad pa cha bzhir bgo //
NK005(ca)004:448: drug dgu dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK005(ca)004:449: de ni gzhi yi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK005(ca)004:450: lnga pa phyed bcas nang ma phan /
NK005(ca)004:451: phyogs bzhir thig bzhi gling dgur phye //
NK005(ca)004:452: nang gi dkyil 'khor dgu yi sa //
NK005(ca)004:453: kun kyang sgo bzhi gru bzhi'i dbus //
NK005(ca)004:454: zlum po zlum po zla gam dang //
NK005(ca)004:455: pad+mo rin chen cha brgyad dang //
NK005(ca)004:456: rgya gram dbyibs te rim pa bzhin //
NK005(ca)004:457: rdor sems rnam snang he ru ka /
NK005(ca)004:458: gar dbang nyi ma rta mchog rnams //
NK005(ca)004:459: dbus dang phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi'o //
NK005(ca)004:460: mda' yab zur nas cha phran gcig /
NK005(ca)004:461: gnyis gcig gnyis dang cha chen gcig /
NK005(ca)004:462: cha chen phyed dang cha phran gcig /
NK005(ca)004:463: bskor ba lha snam pad rdor dang //
NK005(ca)004:465: khor yug nyid do gzhan dag ni //
NK005(ca)004:466: spyi dang mthun par shes bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:467: dkyil chog snga ma rnams su thig gi dbye tshul
NK005(ca)004:468: gsungs pa dag 'bru non dka' bas lag len la
NK005(ca)004:469: 'jug pa bde phyir da lta'i lag len bzhin byas
NK005(ca)004:470: pa'o // gdab pa'i cho ga dang spyod lam ni
NK005(ca)004:471: ye thig gi skabs bzhin 'dir yang shes par bya
NK005(ca)004:473: shar nub byang lho'i thig bzhi'i rjes //
NK005(ca)004:474: logs dang mtshams su gdab par bya //
NK005(ca)004:475: dang por cha chen bcu drug la //
NK005(ca)004:476: zhes sogs gsungs pa'i spyod lam gyis gdab pa'am /
NK005(ca)004:477: spyi dang mthun par btab kyang mi 'gal te dkyil chog bde 'byung de ltar bshad pas so //
NK005(ca)004:478: de ltar las thig rdzogs nas ye thig gi dkyil 'khor bstim nas /
NK005(ca)004:479: thig skud kyi ye shes pa mchod cing bstod nas /
NK005(ca)004:481: de nas lha'i nga rgyal gyi mig gnyis nyi zla'i lta stangs dang rdo rje slong ba'i rgyas /
NK005(ca)004:482: badz+ra be ga a kra ma h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:483: zhes ri mo btegs nas hi zhes sgo'i thig dbyi zhing //
NK005(ca)004:484: thams cad rang bzhin rnam 'phrul mchog /
NK005(ca)004:485: dngos med zhi ba'i 'od ldan gsal //
NK005(ca)004:487: dkyil 'khor dag par byin gyis rlobs //
NK005(ca)004:488: zhes phyogs thams cad mnyam par nyid du blta'o //
NK005(ca)004:490: tshon sna lnga snod so sor blug pa dbus dang phyogs bzhir bzhag /
NK005(ca)004:492: stong pa'i ngang las hi sogs las de bzhin gshegs
NK005(ca)004:493: pa rigs lngar bskyed mig gi blta bas ye shes
NK005(ca)004:494: pa thig gi skabs ltar drangs bstim /
NK005(ca)004:496: sa bon lnga mang du brjod de zhu ba las rin po che'i rdul phra rab tu gyur /
NK005(ca)004:497: badz+ra tsit+ta sa ma ya h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:498: zhes mang du bzlas pas byin gyis brlab /
NK005(ca)004:499: slob dpon gyis h+aum brjod cing rdo rje dang bcas
NK005(ca)004:500: pa'i lag g.yon gyi dbang ldan gyi rtsig pa nang
NK005(ca)004:501: nas dkar mthing dmar ser ljang ba'i re kh+aa lnga
NK005(ca)004:502: sgo tshad gcig tsam bris nas mchod la thod pas
NK005(ca)004:503: bkab ste / 'di ni chos dbyings rnam par dag /
NK005(ca)004:504: sems can khams ni rab sgrol byed //
NK005(ca)004:505: dpal ldan rgyal po rdo rje sems //
NK005(ca)004:506: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi gnas //
NK005(ca)004:507: yang dag bden pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK005(ca)004:508: dkyil 'khor las rnams shis par mdzod //
NK005(ca)004:509: ces bden pa brjod cing btegs nas mtshan ma brtag go //
NK005(ca)004:510: de yang thig phyi nas gdab cing tshon nang nas
NK005(ca)004:511: dgye ste dang por slob dpon dang phyis nas gzhan
NK005(ca)004:513: re kh+aa dma' bas mi 'grub cing //
NK005(ca)004:514: yon pos gdung ba bskyed par byed //
NK005(ca)004:515: chad pas slob dpon slob ma dag /
NK005(ca)004:517: chad lhag las ni nad 'byung zhing //
NK005(ca)004:520: sbom po yis ni nad 'byung zhing //
NK005(ca)004:521: phra na nor rnams zad par 'gyur //
NK005(ca)004:523: zhes gsungs pa ltar shes par byas nas /
NK005(ca)004:524: tshon thob ni pho brang nang ma'i re mig bzhi rigs kyi mdog dang /
NK005(ca)004:525: lho dang lho nub kyi zla gam dmar po /
NK005(ca)004:526: pho brang nang ma'i khyams ni gtso bo'i gnas shar du bzung ba'i phyogs mdog /
NK005(ca)004:527: rtsig pa gtso mdog nang du byas pa'i lnga phrag gam ljang khu /
NK005(ca)004:528: rdo rje'i gdung ser po la gzhi sngon po /
NK005(ca)004:529: re mig gi nang khongs dkar po /
NK005(ca)004:530: khyams sgo ka ba sna tshogs rdo rje'i rwa rnams shar nas rim par dkar sngo dmar ser /
NK005(ca)004:531: rta babs kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga /
NK005(ca)004:534: rdo ra dkar po gzhi sngon po //
NK005(ca)004:538: phyi'i ra ba sngon po ste /
NK005(ca)004:539: lha'i mtshan ma sogs tshon thob gzhan rnams sgrubs thabs las kyang shes pa nyid do //
NK005(ca)004:540: de ltar bri ba rdzogs nas tshon lhag gi ye shes pa mchod cing bstod nas gshegs su gsol /
NK005(ca)004:542: sngar lhag gnas byas pa'i bum pa rnams spos dang
NK005(ca)004:543: rol mos sna drangs te dkyil 'khor gyi byang nas
NK005(ca)004:544: g.yon bskor gyis rang gnas su dgod /
NK005(ca)004:545: gnyis las med na rnam rgyal dbus dang las bum byang sgo'i thad du bzhag /
NK005(ca)004:546: dkyil 'khor gyi mtha' bskor dri bzang gis byug /
NK005(ca)004:547: me tog gi sil ma dgram /
NK005(ca)004:548: phyogs kun tu bla re dang /
NK005(ca)004:551: rgyal mtshan ba dan sna tshogs pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:552: gos zung du ma tshar du dngar bas brgyan cing /
NK005(ca)004:553: me tog dkar po sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)004:554: rdo rje can la sna tshogs pa //
NK005(ca)004:555: 'jig rten dbang la kha dog dkar //
NK005(ca)004:556: ser po mkha' las byung ba la //
NK005(ca)004:557: tsan+dana bdug pa sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)004:558: rdo rje can la du ru ka /
NK005(ca)004:559: spyan ras gzigs la ka bi ta //
NK005(ca)004:560: gu gul rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK005(ca)004:561: mar me'i phreng ba sangs rgyas la //
NK005(ca)004:562: rdo rje can la mar me bdun //
NK005(ca)004:563: spyan ras gzigs la mar me brgya //
NK005(ca)004:564: stong ni rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK005(ca)004:565: sangs rgyas rnam la tsan+dana dri //
NK005(ca)004:566: rdo rje can la gur gum yin //
NK005(ca)004:567: spyan ras gzigs la tsan+dana dmar //
NK005(ca)004:568: ga bur rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK005(ca)004:569: me tog phreng ba bdug pa kun //
NK005(ca)004:570: de bzhin mar me thams cad dang //
NK005(ca)004:571: spos rnams thams cad ji snyed pa //
NK005(ca)004:574: zhal zas kyi khyad par yang /
NK005(ca)004:575: kha ba tsha ba rdo rjer 'bul //
NK005(ca)004:576: mngar ba rdo rje rtag pa la //
NK005(ca)004:577: skyur ba rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK005(ca)004:578: de bzhin lan tsh+wa 'jig rten rjer //
NK005(ca)004:579: rta yi rgyal por thams cad dam //
NK005(ca)004:580: bska ba rab tu rtag par bya //
NK005(ca)004:581: zhes gsungs pa'i mtshan nyid can gyi mchod pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:582: gtor ma'i khyad par ci 'byor pa dag byin gyis brlabs te dgod par bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:583: de yang rdo rje can ni he ru ka dang /
NK005(ca)004:584: rdo rje 'dzin rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK005(ca)004:585: spyan ras gzigs gar dbang ngo //
NK005(ca)004:586: gnyis pa la rang don dang gzhan don sgrub pa gnyis kyi /
NK005(ca)004:587: dang po la sngon du bya ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:588: sgrub mchod dngos dang dbang bskur ba'o //
NK005(ca)004:589: dang po la spyi dang khyad par gyi sbyor ba gnyis las /
NK005(ca)004:591: de nas rdo rje rgyal po dang rgyal thebs dang
NK005(ca)004:592: phyag rgya dang brda' sbyor dang rdul phyags sogs so
NK005(ca)004:593: sor phye ste gdan bshams pa la 'khod nas /
NK005(ca)004:597: yul mchog dman la tshogs bsag pa /
NK005(ca)004:602: mchod rdzas brlab pa rnams te sgrub thabs bzhin no //
NK005(ca)004:604: sta gon gyi lha dgod pa /
NK005(ca)004:606: brda' phyag bya ba dang gsum las /
NK005(ca)004:607: dang po ni mdun gyi dkyil 'khor bsang sbyangs /
NK005(ca)004:608: stong pa'i ngang las srung 'khor gzhal yas khang lha'i
NK005(ca)004:609: gdan dang bcas pa mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su
NK005(ca)004:610: rdzogs pa la / lha'i mtshan ma rnams lha tshogs su gyur pa ni /
NK005(ca)004:611: dkyil 'khor dbus ma'i lte bar rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:612: phyogs bzhir bde mchog ma sogs nas /
NK005(ca)004:613: g.yas bskor du 'khod kyi bar dang /
NK005(ca)004:614: dkyil 'khor shar ma'i dbus su rgyal ba rtag pa yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:615: phyogs bzhir sangs rgyas kun brjod ma sogs so //
NK005(ca)004:616: dkyil 'khor lho ma'i dbus su he ru ka yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:617: phyogs bzhir goo r+ai ma sogs so //
NK005(ca)004:618: dkyil 'khor nub ma'i dbus su pad+ma gar dbang yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:619: phyogs bzhir rnam gzigs ma sogs /
NK005(ca)004:620: dkyil 'khor byang ma'i dbus su rdo rje nyi ma yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:621: phyogs bzhir dbang bskur ma sogs /
NK005(ca)004:622: mtshams bzhi'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su rta mchog yab yum dang /
NK005(ca)004:623: g.yas g.yon du sna tshogs pad+mo sogs nas /
NK005(ca)004:624: rigs dang mtshungs par snang ba'o //
NK005(ca)004:626: de ltar gdod nas rnam dag dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor mngon sum du grub par gyur /
NK005(ca)004:627: snying ga'i sa bon las 'od zer 'phros pas nam
NK005(ca)004:628: mkhar bzhugs pa'i sta gon gyi dkyil 'khor thams cad
NK005(ca)004:631: rta mchog gi snying po bzla zhing phyi 'brang gi bgegs bskrad /
NK005(ca)004:632: h+aum bzhi pa'i sngags kyi rdo rje gsor ba dang bcas srung 'khor gyi sgo dbye /
NK005(ca)004:633: ma h+aa sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK005(ca)004:634: lan gnyis kyis mchod yon phul /
NK005(ca)004:635: ma h+aa su kha h+aum gi bar tshogs zhing gi skabs ltar mchod /
NK005(ca)004:636: 'khor los bsgyur ba drug gi sngags mthar /
NK005(ca)004:637: a be sha ya a dzahh+aum bam hoh zhes brtags pa rol mo'i sgra dang bcas pas /
NK005(ca)004:638: ye shes kyi lha rnams gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la gnyis su med par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)004:642: dzahh+aum bam hoh pra be sha ya phata /
NK005(ca)004:643: a la la hoh zhes tshad med pa bzhi'i 'jug
NK005(ca)004:644: pas dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bzhi nas sgo bzhi phye
NK005(ca)004:645: bas rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor du mngon
NK005(ca)004:646: sum du bzhugs par bsam mo //
NK005(ca)004:648: +aahh+aum a ti p+au hoh sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+han d+ha nam k+aa ro mi /
NK005(ca)004:649: a la la hoh mo a ti b+h+au h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:651: sarba ta th+aa ga ta sa ma yo ga sid+d+hi a h+aum /
NK005(ca)004:652: zhes lha dang bdag rang bzhin gnyis med du rtogs par brda phyag bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:654: +aa h+aum zhes pas rang nyid rdo rje sems dpa'
NK005(ca)004:655: mdun bskyed dang ro gcig tu 'dres par bsam mo
NK005(ca)004:656: // skabs 'dir gdug pa can 'dul ba'i phyir ma
NK005(ca)004:657: tam sgrol ba'i cho ga byed par gsungs pa bzhin
NK005(ca)004:658: spro na h+aum mdzad kyi dkyil chog dang rigs mthun
NK005(ca)004:659: gyi cho ga gzhan nas kyang blangs pas khyab bo
NK005(ca)004:660: // // de ltar khyad par gyi sbyor ba rnams
NK005(ca)004:661: ni sgrub mchod kyi nyin dang po kho na'i bya
NK005(ca)004:662: // // ba'o // gnyis pa la dkyil 'khor sgrub pa /
NK005(ca)004:664: dbang len pa dang gsum gyi /
NK005(ca)004:668: sbyor ba'i ting nge 'dzin gsum gyis dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor bskyed par bshad pa bzhin /
NK005(ca)004:669: 'di ltar dmigs pa'i yul bral sems kyi dbyings //
NK005(ca)004:671: rta mchog gi dkyil 'khor rnams la dbang bskur ba'i bar sgrub thabs bzhin te /
NK005(ca)004:674: sgrub chos rten dang brten pa'i dkyil 'khor gcig gis bsdus pa bdag mdun dbyer med du bsgom zhing /
NK005(ca)004:675: dkyil chog rnying ba gnyis las dngos gzhi'i skabs su
NK005(ca)004:676: bum pa logs sgrub kyi gsal kha ma gsungs pa
NK005(ca)004:677: bdag mdun bum gsum dbyer med du sgrub pa la
NK005(ca)004:678: dgongs pa bzhin shes par bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:680: rang nyid dkyil 'khor gyi gtso bo las rdo rje
NK005(ca)004:681: sems dpa' zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa'i rnam pas thon
NK005(ca)004:682: nas phyag mchod sogs la 'jug par mos te /
NK005(ca)004:683: phyag dang mchod pa bstod pa snga ma'i mthar thug pa'i bar byas nas /
NK005(ca)004:684: rigs drug gi rol mo'i mchod pa'ang spro na skabs 'dir bya ste gzhan las shes par 'gyur la /
NK005(ca)004:685: de nas 'dzab khang dbye ba sogs bzlas pa'i rnal 'byor rnams dang /
NK005(ca)004:686: dbang dang 'brel na rtsa ba'i bzlas pa'i rjes su
NK005(ca)004:687: bum pa'i gzungs thag la brten nas bzlas pa ci
NK005(ca)004:689: bzlas pa'i mthar mchod bstod bshags pa ste skabs kyi mjug bsdu ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:693: dag pa dran pa rnams ji ltar nus pa sgrub
NK005(ca)004:694: thabs kyi gzhung bzhin byas nas rnal 'byor pa rnams
NK005(ca)004:695: rgyan dang bcas pas rdor dril thogs nas yi ge
NK005(ca)004:696: brgya ba brjod bzhin du stangs stabs kyis dkyil 'khor
NK005(ca)004:698: slar yang rang gnas su langs te 'khod pas gzugs
NK005(ca)004:699: brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la ye shes kyi 'khor lo
NK005(ca)004:700: byin 'bebs pa dang gnas dang dkyil 'khor mnga' gsol
NK005(ca)004:701: ba rnams kyang bya bar gsungs so //
NK005(ca)004:702: de nas gtor ma'i cho ga ni sgrub thabs su
NK005(ca)004:703: bshad pa'i lhag gtor nyid skabs ji lta ba'i bsgyur
NK005(ca)004:704: kha shes pas phyi rol gtor ma'i tshul du skabs
NK005(ca)004:706: bdag 'jug ste dbang chog las shes shing sgru mchod
NK005(ca)004:707: tsam la bdag 'jug ma grub kyang mi 'gal mod
NK005(ca)004:708: spyir 'grub na legs pa ni yin no //
NK005(ca)004:709: gsum pa gzhan don dbang bskur ba'i rim pa yang
NK005(ca)004:710: dbang chog logs su bkod pa las shes par bya'o
NK005(ca)004:711: // gsum pa rjes kyi cho ga la /
NK005(ca)004:714: brtan ma skyong ba gsum ni sgrub thabs kyi dkyus bzhin te /
NK005(ca)004:715: h+aum mdzad kyis mkha' 'gro ma bskyang ba zhes skabs
NK005(ca)004:716: 'dir gsungs pa yang brtan skyong las gzhan du med
NK005(ca)004:717: do // bzhi pa ni dkyil 'khor nyer bsdu'i tshe /
NK005(ca)004:718: gtang rag gi mchod pa bshams shing byin gyis brlabs
NK005(ca)004:719: nas 'bul ba dang bstod pa rgyas bsdus ci rigs
NK005(ca)004:720: pas bstod / yi ge brgya bas lhag chad bskang zhing bzod par gsol /
NK005(ca)004:721: ras bris kyi dkyil 'khor yin na ye shes pa brtan bzhugs dang /
NK005(ca)004:722: dam tshig gi dkyil 'khor gsal btab /
NK005(ca)004:723: h+aum zhes pas rang gi snying ga'i 'od kyis dkyil 'khor gyi 'khor lo bsdus la /
NK005(ca)004:724: go bgo lus bsrung sogs sgrub thabs ltar bya /
NK005(ca)004:725: rdul tshon la brten pa'i sgrub mchod zhag sbrel du
NK005(ca)004:726: byed pa'i nyin snga ma rnams la yang de bzhin
NK005(ca)004:727: no // gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gshegs gsol byed na /
NK005(ca)004:728: skabs 'dir las kyi rdo rjes sbyin sreg dang bskang bshags kyang 'grub tu rung na bya zhing /
NK005(ca)004:729: thams cad kyis dkyil 'khor bskor zhing smon lam gdab /
NK005(ca)004:730: yi ge brgya pas lhag chad bskang zhing bshags pa bya /
NK005(ca)004:731: shis pa brjod cing dngos grub blangs /
NK005(ca)004:732: slar yang mchod cing bstod nas bro gar dang rdo rje'i glus dgyes pa bskyed /
NK005(ca)004:733: de nas be g+aa kra ma yam /
NK005(ca)004:734: zhes pa ye shes kyi 'khor lo mdun gyi nam
NK005(ca)004:735: mkhar btegs la gtang rag gi mchod bstod bzod gsol
NK005(ca)004:737: khyed kyis sems can don kun mdzad //
NK005(ca)004:739: gats+tsha muhzhesa ye shes pa gshegs /
NK005(ca)004:740: dam tshig pa sngar bzhin bsdus nas go bgo zhing lus bsrung ba byas la /
NK005(ca)004:741: chos thams cad skye med du mos nas /
NK005(ca)004:742: a k+aa ro bzla zhing rdo rje dang bcas pa'i
NK005(ca)004:743: lag pas thog ma lha mtshan nas cung zad blangs
NK005(ca)004:745: lhag ma dbang ldan nas brtsams te gtso gnas kyi
NK005(ca)004:746: bar du phyags pa bum pa la sogs pa'i snod
NK005(ca)004:747: du bsdus pa dngos grub kyi don du 'jog pa'am
NK005(ca)004:748: chu bo chen por bkur bsti dang bcas pas gshegs
NK005(ca)004:749: nas dkyil 'khor gyi rjes mi mngon par byas /
NK005(ca)004:750: phur bu'i khro bo bcu mchod nas bsdu /
NK005(ca)004:751: cod pan bkrol te khrus bya /
NK005(ca)004:753: slar yang gtor ma bshams te mgron spyi dang khyad
NK005(ca)004:754: par gyi srung ma rnams dang rten la bzhag pa'i
NK005(ca)004:755: rgyal po bzhi dang phyogs skyong la bsgos nas gshegs
NK005(ca)004:756: su gsol / slar yang shis brjod dang mchod sbyin
NK005(ca)004:757: smon lam gdab pa rnams byas na spyod lam gyi
NK005(ca)004:759: spyi don gsum pa grub pa 'bras bu'i tshul la /
NK005(ca)004:761: des grub pa'i tshad bstan pa ste sgrub thabs su bshad pa bzhin no //
NK005(ca)004:762: tshul 'di la rgyud 'grel dang sgrub dkyil sogs yig rnying ngo mtshar can du ma yod mod /
NK005(ca)004:764: rdor sems kyi dkyil 'khor gyi sgo nas bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:765: rnam snang gar dbang nyi ma rnams kyi sgo nas zhi ba dang /
NK005(ca)004:767: rgyas pa'i las kyi nye bar bsnyen pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:768: he ru ka'i sgo nas drag po'i phrin las kyis sgrub pa dang /
NK005(ca)004:769: de dag gi mthar sgrub pa chen po'i las kyis
NK005(ca)004:770: dngos grub len pa ste smin slob sgrub chen kho
NK005(ca)004:771: na'i dbang du mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK005(ca)004:772: deng dus sgrub chen gyi 'dra 'bag sgrub mchod dang
NK005(ca)004:773: dbang rkyang tsam sgrub pa la lag tu len dka'
NK005(ca)004:774: bas / yul dus kyi rkyen dang 'tshams pa'i dbang
NK005(ca)004:775: du byas pa ni 'di tsam ste gzhan du smin
NK005(ca)004:776: slob kyi tshul du sgrub pa sogs so so'i gnas
NK005(ca)004:777: skabs kyi bye brag shes pas dam pa snga ma
NK005(ca)004:778: rnams kyi legs par bshad pa'i gsung rab la rnam
NK005(ca)004:779: par spyod pa'i blo gros kyis 'jug par bya'o //
NK005(ca)004:780: phul byung dgos grub rin chen gyis gang ba'i //
NK005(ca)004:781: zab yangs rgyud sde'i mtsho ngos mthong tsam gyis //
NK005(ca)004:782: don gnyer 'dod pa'i yid ni g.yos gyur kyang //
NK005(ca)004:783: nyam chung mthu yis gya tshom nyid du ci //
NK005(ca)004:784: 'on kyang ded dpon mkhas pa'i bshes gnyen dang //
NK005(ca)004:785: lhag bsam ba dan spro ba'i rlung shugs kyis //
NK005(ca)004:786: bskul bas yid bzhin 'dod 'jo'i rin po che //
NK005(ca)004:787: cha tsam thob 'di ci phyir skal bzang min //
NK005(ca)004:788: gangs ri'i khrod 'dir sngon byon mkhas rnams kyis //
NK005(ca)004:789: ha cang rgyas dang rigs 'gres sbyar ba las //
NK005(ca)004:790: 'jug bde rang gzhung tshugs par ma bkrol bas //
NK005(ca)004:791: tshul 'dir 'jug la btang snyoms bgyid ma spobs //
NK005(ca)004:792: phyogs lhung rna ba'i bu ga 'khyog po ni //
NK005(ca)004:793: sngon med legs bshad gsar pa'i 'brog dgon te //
NK005(ca)004:794: de lta mod kyi bdag yid dge goms phyir //
NK005(ca)004:795: brjod pa'i bsod nams 'gro la gsal gyur cig /
NK005(ca)004:796: bdag kyang tshe rabs kun tu rgyal ba yi //
NK005(ca)004:797: bstan la rjes zhugs thugs kyi gsang ba'i mdzod //
NK005(ca)004:798: yongs bzung gsang chen bstan pa rgyas byed cing //
NK005(ca)004:799: rigs drug 'khor los sgyur ba'i gnas thob shog /
NK005(ca)004:800: ces sangs rgyas thams cad mnyam par sbyor ba'i dkyil
NK005(ca)004:801: 'khor gyi cho ga kun tu bzang po'i zhal lung
NK005(ca)004:802: zhes bya ba / rig pa 'dzin pa 'gyur med
NK005(ca)004:803: rdo rjes brjod bde'i ngag gis snying por dril te
NK005(ca)004:804: chu pho rta'i lo la o rgyan smin grol gling
